body.name: Steam Cleaner, 2500W High Pressure Steam Cleaner for Home, Steamer for Cleaning with 3 Brush Heads and Extended Rod, Handheld Steam Cleaner for Upholstery, Kitchen, Bathroom, Grout and Tile
features: 💧【Powerful Steamer for Cleaning】Working 2500 watts, this high temperature steamer can emit 105℃（221℉）high pressured flow of steam blast that is excessively powerful to deeply clean out the hard, sticky grease easily and thoroughly! This steam cleaner for upholstery does save your time and boost your efficiency! Do not let go of any dead corner!

💧【10s Fast Heating, No Waiting!】Just aim the steamer at the stain, then turn on the power button and wait for about 10 seconds! The steamer for cleaning will spray strong pressured steam up to 105℃. Steam cleaner for car keeps heating while using to maintain its heat and keep the steam strong and continuous, which is different from other steam cleaners for home use that need a break every 2 minutes to reheat and rebuild the pressure.

💧【3 Brush Heads, 8.6 inch extended】The steam cleaner comes equipped with 3 different brush heads and extended rod, long cables. The various brush heads cater to different surfaces like carpets, grout, and upholstery, ensuring a comprehensive cleaning experience. The extension pole helps reach high or distant areas with ease, making it convenient for cleaning ceilings, curtains, or other elevated surfaces.

💧【1000ML Large Capacity Water Tank】The portable steam cleaner can be used continuously for about 1 hour, no need to add water frequently, improving your cleaning work efficiency. ⚡This Handheld steam cleaner doesn't have a trigger so when you press the on button,make sure it is aimed away from you and the waterproof washer is properly installed , ideally at it's intended target.⚡

💧【Multi-Use Steam Cleaner】Are you looking for a high pressure steam cleaner to use for multiple areas? Our steam cleaner is a good choice for you. Not only this handheld steamer is used for cleaning away the dirty and stains on the kitchen, bathroom, floor, grout, tile, carpet, but also can serve for car detailing, which will save you a ton more on car wash! With 3 different brush heads, this furniture steam cleaner is also suitable for cleaning various surfaces such as stoves, walls, sofa,etc.
